data.description: LOCATION!! LOCATION!! LOCATION!! HUGE DOUBLE LOT OPPORTUNITY. 1BR/1BATH SINGLE FAMILY HOME!!! CLEAN, IMPROVED BATHROOM, NEW ELECTRIC STOVE AND WATER HEATER, PORCELAIN FLOORS ALL AROUND. NEW CENTRAL AIR CONDITIONING SYSTEM THERE IS AN OVERSIZED LIVING ROOM, A SMALL DINING ROOM, FULLY RENOVATED MODERN OPEN KITCHEN WITH HIGH CABINETS AND SOLID COUNTERTOPS. YOUR BACKYARD HAS HUGE SHADE TREES, PLENTY OF SPACE TO ENJOY AND PLENTY OF GRASS FOR THE KIDS AND PETS TO RUN AND PLAY!!! YOU CAN EVEN DRIVE DOWN THE BACK ALLEY AND ENTER YOUR BACKYARD FOR PRIVATE PARKING OR TRAILER PARKING. AND IT COULD BE A GREAT OPPORTUNITY FOR AN INVESTOR OR BUILDER. , THEY ONLY GO ON SHOWTIME.
